<strong><em>Important:</em></strong> The address label template must have been <a href="/en/order-processing/fulfilment/generating-documents#400">created</a> in the <strong>System » Orders » Documents » Address label</strong> menu beforehand. Whether the primary invoice address or the primary delivery address of the contact will be printed, depends on the setting in the address label template.</p></td>
