<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Documents</strong> view, activate the documents that you want to delete or activate the option next to <strong>File name</strong> to activate all documents and save them afterwards. After you have confirmed your decision by clicking on <strong>Delete</strong>, the activated documents will be deleted and removed from the overview.</p>
