<h3 id="2100">12.3. Deleting bank data</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Delete the bank data of your contact if they are outdated.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Deleting bank data:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
